  "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\n\r\nIn altair when processing a block, we update balances multiple time and every time we update BeaconState tree root due to the hook, this is inefficient.\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\n\r\nUpdate balances on a cloned balances tree and once it's done, we escalate the change to BeaconState tree root\r\n\r\nIn `CachedBalanceList`\r\n\r\n```ts\r\nconstructor(type: BasicListType<List<number>>, tree: Tree) {\r\n    this.type = type;\r\n    // this.persistentTree always link to the parent tree, this.tree may belong to the parent tree or a cloned tree\r\n    this.tree = tree;\r\n    this.persistentTree = tree;\r\n  }\r\n  \r\n  // all methods should work on this.tree\r\n\r\n  asTransient(): void {\r\n    // from this time all increaseBalances should work on a cloned tree, this will not update the BeaconState parent tree\r\n    this.tree = this.persistentTree.clone();\r\n    // the persistent-ts list, may remove later\r\n    this.persistent.asTransient();\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  asPersistent: void {\r\n    // updating the root of persistentTree would escalate the change to BeaconState tree root due to the hook\r\n    this.persistentTree.root = this.tree.root;\r\n    // the persistent-ts list, may remove later\r\n    this.tree = this.persistentTree;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  // may need to update Proxy\r\n```\r\n",
